'''Sak<U+0131>zl<U+0131> Ahmed Esat Pasha''' (1828 [[Sak<U+0131>z]]-1875 [[Izmir]]) was an [[Ottoman Empire|Ottoman]] [[statesman]]. He was [[Grand Vizier|Grand Vizier of the Ottoman Empire]] during two terms:
* 15 March, 1873 - 15 April, 1873
* 26 April, 1875 - 26 August, 1875. <ref>http://rulers.org/rult.html#turkey</ref>

